        "about_content": "<b>The New Address of Luxury and Comfort in the Heart of the Black Sea</b><br><br>Rising in one of the most prestigious spots of Batumi, SKY TOWER Hotel offers its guests not just an accommodation, but an unforgettable experience blended with the unique nature of the Black Sea. Our hotel, which draws attention with its modern architecture and central location, provides both peace and city life together with its proximity to the coastline and a distance of only 50 meters to Ardagani Lake.<br><br><b>Panoramic Views and Stylish Accommodation</b><br>All our rooms are specially designed for our guests to start the day with the endless blue of the Black Sea or the calming view of Ardagani Lake. In our rooms where stylish decoration meets technology; all modern equipments such as air conditioning, flat-screen satellite TV, work desk and minibar are offered as standard. In order to carry your comfort to the highest level, luxury bathrobes, slippers and special toiletries are meticulously prepared in our bathrooms.<br><br><b>Relax Your Soul: Spa and Wellness</b><br>For our guests who want to get away from the pace of the city, our fully equipped Spa center provides service all day long. You can be renewed under the guidance of our expert staff and relieve the tiredness of the day with a pleasant drink in our specially designed bar.<br><br><b>Privileged Services and Location</b><br>We have thought of every detail to make you feel at home with our 24-hour reception focusing on guest satisfaction, our free WiFi access and our private parking on site.<br><br><b>Central Location Advantages:</b><br>• Ardagani Lake: 50 Meters<br>• Dolphinarium: 1.3 km<br>• Batumi Archaeological Museum: 1.9 km<br>• Batumi International Airport: 4 km",
